bb2329b37774cadcfedb8","tid":1192510,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:53:52.000Z","msg":"-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82b693b6f1e750b8f1df80ec8c5b5633aa14ddb8","tid":1192510,"uid":41389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f85c8898be593410865e4cf7f485de8f106af466","tid":1192510,"uid":150651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"又熱又著制服<br />\n又要維持秩序 保障大家既安全<br />\n希望聽日大家行過見佢地辛苦既 比支水送上愛心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"送屎尿水？"},{"pid":"0f7e1b06d747868394d4bbcfa30223f93396978a","tid":1192510,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"82b693b6f1e750b8f1df80ec8c5b5633aa14ddb8","tid":1192510,"uid":41389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f85c8898be593410865e4cf7f485de8f106af466","tid":1192510,"uid":150651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"又熱又著制服<br />\n又要維持秩序 保障大家既安全<br />\n希望聽日大家行過見佢地辛苦既 比支水送上愛心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"送屎尿水？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"打份工，各爲其主。"},{"pid":"9170fce7dd9a4251cfc45dc00739509a530455b3","tid":1192510,"uid":25754,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"我煮左生炒骨，腐乳通菜同牛仔骨俾警察叔叔食"},{"pid":"068e8b931a821fc53361c7e34faea037d6e693ac","tid":1192510,"uid":97949,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f85c8898be593410865e4cf7f485de8f106af466","tid":1192510,"uid":150651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"又熱又著制服<br />\n又要維持秩序 保障大家既安全<br />\n希望聽日大家行過見佢地辛苦既 比支水送上愛心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"送你老母 警犬冇糧出？"},{"pid":"4bc133b639bb32dba6aa68